&lt;li&gt;Develop audience segmentation using firmographic and behavioral data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously test and optimize through A/B and multivariate experiments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Campaign Execution&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
