&lt;p&gt;As a Revenue Strategy Analyst, you will be the analytical engine behind AfterShip&#39;s GTM strategy, turning data into the decisions that shape how we grow. Reporting to the Senior Manager, Revenue Operations, you will partner across Sales, Marketing, Partnerships, Customer Success, Finance, and Data to uncover insights, optimize revenue-driving processes, and accelerate company OKRs through rigorous, data-informed thinking.&lt;/p&gt;
