&lt;li&gt;Partner with Solutions Architects on enablement programs relevant to their pre-sales motions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish metrics to measure the effectiveness of enablement initiatives and track impact on sales performance and revenue growth&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
