&lt;p&gt;Your job is not just to close deals. It is to define where we should play, how we win, and ensure we follow through.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What success looks like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
