&lt;li&gt;Support early affiliate activation workflows, including creator matching and campaign setup basics where relevant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run weekly merchant check-ins, track blockers, escalate product and integration issues, and maintain launch trackers.&lt;/li&gt;
